## Round 3 — 2026-06-12 — convergence check on v3

Internal Claude red team (convergence check). Tally with external CLIs: **3 ADVANCE / 2 ANOTHER ROUND**.

### Reviewer A — Product Skeptic — ANOTHER ROUND
- (1) degraded synthesis RESOLVED; (2) promotion rule RESOLVED; (3) reframed model RESOLVED.
- New issues: P7 "no open contradiction" depends on deferred contradiction detection (blocker —
  flag the dependency or define v1 fallback); §3 metric "share of trusted claims backed by a
  trusted source" is ~tautological under P7; machine-generated caveats are load-bearing but deferred.

### Reviewer B — Technical Realist — ADVANCE
- All three collisions RESOLVED. Promotion rule implementable as written; the contradiction-detection
  dependency is *acceptable at the vision layer* (commits to what the gate decides on, not mechanism;
  P5 already makes conflicts first-class). Remaining items sub-vision-layer / Architecture's problem.

### Reviewer C — Market Cynic — ADVANCE
- Round-2 "no testable product" RESOLVED by the read-only `dossier show` view + degraded synthesis;
  the wedge is now demonstrable in session one. Two residual GTM concerns (CLI is a thin vehicle for
  the wedge; session-one shows the weakest version of the differentiator) are Feature-Spec/sequencing
  risks, not unsettled vision questions.

### External CLIs
- **codex — ANOTHER ROUND:** (1)(2) RESOLVED, (3) PARTIAL. Blocker: immutable run reports
  ("never rewritten") vs. P5 "surface conflicts wherever rendered (run reports, dossier view)" —
  reports can't be both frozen artifacts and live surfaces; plus "confidence-gated ingestion" vs
  P1 "ingestion is unconditional" terminology.
- **gemini — ADVANCE:** all collisions resolved; no new contradictions; structurally sound.

### Disposition (v4)
All round-3 findings are precision/wording fixes, not structural. Applied in v4: run reports are
immutable snapshots (current conflicts live in the dossier view); rendering contract scoped to
claim-derived rendering; "gated promotion" terminology; honest contradiction-detection dependency
flag; success metric de-tautologized. **Convergence reached** — remaining feedback is operational,
not structural.

